%% state-machine: connection/lifecycle
stateDiagram-v2
  state initial
  state handshaking
  state connected
  state closing
  state draining
  state closed
  initial --> handshaking: connection_started
  handshaking --> connected: handshake_completed
  connected --> closing: connection_close_sent
  initial --> draining: connection_close_received
  handshaking --> draining: connection_close_received
  connected --> draining: connection_close_received
  closing --> closed: connection_close_timer_expired
  draining --> closed: connection_close_timer_expired
  handshaking --> closed: idle_timeout_expired
  connected --> closed: idle_timeout_expired
